data.description: The perfect low-maintenance condo in one of OKC's most desirable complexes!   The two-story property offers a versatile floor plan and includes 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths upstairs and a 1/2 bath on lower level.  Both bedrooms feature walk-in closets and ensuite bathrooms.  Unit also includes a private outdoor courtyard between home and 2 car attached garage.  The Sutton Place complex is conveniently located near Uptown Grocery, shopping, and restaurants, has easy access to the Hefner Parkway, and includes security guard house and pool.  Don't miss your chance to make this one yours!
